.

Shots from last nights Battle Dome session, going live in a few weeks Sunday nights 7-11pm EST on Twitch.tv/NRDForge 
BEWARE OF CHICKENS!

Tasked by the mayor of Minescraftin to slay this Skeleton fiend that was being held at bay by the townspeople on the island keep; they had collapsed the bridges at all the crossings to the island. 
At first they believed they were safe from any further danger as the current was too strong to swim across! The destruction this creature had caused as it tore through their small town left them in ruins... the worst thing imaginable happened as skeletal wings unfold from the creature and it begins to test the waters, though it is unable to maintain flight long.
That’s where our party came in to save the day and get paid for it! 
BONUS! 🥳🤩🤘🎲

caption.text:
Eight teams competed in the Season Two playoffs of Overwatch League with a $3.5 million prize pool on the line.

The teams competed across the entire month of September in a double elimination bracket before the final two teams made their way to the Wells Fargo Center in Philadelphia. 
The reigning champions London Spitfire were eliminated early in their quest to repeat as champions, dropping to New York Excelsior 4-1 in the first round, and then getting swept by the San Francisco Shock in the losers’ round
.
.
.
.
